This is the Smart Keywording Plugin for ResourceSpace by Kreuzverweis.

= License =
Apache 2.0

= Building =
If you are on a non-Windows System, just run packme.sh on the command line
to create a working ResourceSpace plugin package. The script stores it at ../smartkeywording.rsp.

= Installation =
Use the Plugin-Manager to upload the plugin, then activate it.
The plugin replaces the editing UI for resource fields with the shortname 'keywords'.
For the plugin to work correctly, the 'keywords' field must be of type textarea. 

= System Requirements =
Please check the plugin's website for the requirements on the server where you
install the plugin. 